Uses of Package
edu.rit.m2mp

Packages that use edu.rit.m2mp
edu.rit.m2mp.debug Package edu.rit.m2mp.debug contains channels useful for debugging an M2MP application. 
edu.rit.m2mp.ip Package edu.rit.m2mp.ip contains Many-to-Many Protocol (M2MP) channel implementations that use UDP datagrams to convey M2MP packets. 
 

Classes in edu.rit.m2mp used by edu.rit.m2mp.debug
Channel
          Interface Channel specifies the interface for a channel in the Many-to-Many Protocol (M2MP).
 

Classes in edu.rit.m2mp used by edu.rit.m2mp.ip
Channel
          Interface Channel specifies the interface for a channel in the Many-to-Many Protocol (M2MP).
ChannelAddress
          Interface ChannelAddress is a tagging interface for a channel address in the Many-to-Many Protocol (M2MP).
